            Graphic: Hamilton County Sheriff's Office Patrol Car.
   __________________________________________________________________

   This department monitors all courts in Hamilton County for DUI
   offenders. Instruct these people where to go to pay for and schedule
   their DUI School. Work with the D.A.'s office, the Judges and Police
   Officers to insure all DUI cases are handled properly.
     __________________________________________________________________

                           Performance Objectives

   [bluearrow.gif] Collect tuition for DUI School.

     [bluearrow.gif] Schedule DUI School.

     [bluearrow.gif] Coordinate with State on issue of restricted drivers
   license.
     * The Hamilton County Sheriff's Office DUI School is a Tennessee
       accredited program.
     * The DUI School is a one day program, it is usually held on the
       first Saturday of the month.
     * The DUI School office is in the Hamilton County/Chattanooga Courts
       Building located at 600 Market Street on the ground floor room
       G-29.
     * The office hours are 8:00am to 4:00 pm Monday thru Friday.
     * For more information you may contact the DUI School office at the
       above listed numbers.




